You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead. Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision. Rear camera - Watching your back! description:
The 2023 Genesis G80 2.5T stands out as a luxury sedan that blends refined design, performance, comfort, and advanced features. With its elegant exterior, all-wheel drive confidence, and modern interior amenities, this G80 delivers a premium driving experience for owners who appreciate quality, sophistication, and versatility.
Standout Attributes

Body style: 4-door sedan

Exterior color: White

Drivetrain: All-Wheel Drive (AWD)

Engine: 2.5L 4-cylinder (turbocharged - standard for the 2.5T)

Series / Trim: 2.5T

Transmission: 8-Speed Automatic

This combination offers a balance of power, efficiency, and all-season traction - ideal for a variety of climates and driving conditions.

Performance & Drive Dynamics

Turbocharged 2.5-liter 4-cylinder engine delivers a strong, responsive ride while maintaining efficiency and smoothness.

8-speed automatic transmission ensures refined gear changes and a comfortable driving feel.

All-Wheel Drive provides enhanced stability and traction - especially useful in rain, snow, or varying road conditions.

Suspension and chassis tuning typical of the G80 give a balanced ride: refined yet capable of confident handling, combining comfort and control.

Whether you're commuting, driving across long distances, or navigating city streets, this G80 2.5T offers a compelling mix of performance and composure.

nterior Comfort & Luxury

Inside, the G80 2.5T brings a premium cabin environment with comfort and sophistication:

Spacious seating for driver and passengers with a well-appointed interior.

High-quality materials and finishes providing an upscale feel - soft surfaces, quality trim, and attention to detail.

Power-adjustable front seats (with typical features like lumbar support), offering comfort and customization for the driver (and often front passenger, depending on packages).

Generous rear-seat space - ideal for comfort on long journeys or chauffeured rides.

Climate control system (dual-zone or more, depending on package) for personalized comfort for front and rear occupants.

Ample trunk and cargo space for a full-size luxury sedan, combining practicality with luxury.

Quiet cabin insulation and sound-deadening - giving a serene, refined ride.




At INFINITI on Camelback you can enjoy the purchase experience and Buy with Total Confidence. All of our vehicles come with a Minimum 135 point inspection! Giving you Total Peace of Mind when choosing the vehicle that's right for you. INFINITI on Camelback providing Luxury within Reach.

You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. description:
Experience the exceptional 2024 Chevrolet Blazer LT, a versatile and dynamic SUV that combines style, performance, and advanced technology. This stunning Red Blazer LT is equipped with a powerful 3.6L V6 SIDI engine, seamlessly paired with a 9-Speed Automatic transmission and All-Wheel Drive, delivering an impressive blend of power and efficiency with an EPA-estimated 18 MPG in the city and 26 MPG on the highway.

. Driver Confidence Package
. Midnight/Sport Edition
. Preferred Equipment Group 3LT
. Chevrolet Infotainment 3 Plus System with 6-Speaker Audio
. Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
. 8-Way Power Driver's Seat with Lumbar Support
. Heated Front Seats
. Leather-Appointed Seating
. Power Liftgate
. Lane Change Alert with Side Blind Zone Alert
. Rear Cross Traffic Alert
. Rear Park Assist with Audible Warning

The Blazer LT's bold and refined exterior design, complemented by the Midnight/Sport Edition and sleek 18-inch Grazen Metallic Aluminum wheels, creates a striking presence on the road. Step inside and experience the premium Perforated Leather-Appointed Seating, which offers exceptional comfort and style. The Chevrolet Infotainment 3 Plus System, with its intuitive 8-inch touchscreen, seamlessly integrates your smartphone via Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, providing a seamless and connected driving experience.

Safety and convenience are paramount in the Blazer LT, with features like the Driver Confidence Package, which includes Lane Change Alert with Side Blind Zone Alert and Rear Cross Traffic Alert, keeping you aware of your surroundings. The Rear Park Assist with Audible Warning ensures confident maneuvering, while the Power Liftgate provides effortless access to the spacious cargo area.

Whether you're embarking on a family adventure, commuting in style, or seeking a versatile SUV that can handle your active lifestyle, the 2024 Chevrolet Blazer LT is the perfect choice. Experience the exceptional craftsmanship, advanced technology, and exceptional performance that make this Blazer LT a standout in its class.

Schedule a test drive today and discover the exceptional value and driving experience that the 2024 Chevrolet Blazer LT has to offer.

Enjoy the signature John Cooper Works style and 18-inch JCW Lap Spoke 2-Tone wheels with summer tires for a sporty look and agile performance. This MINI is the perfect blend of sporty design, cutting-edge tech, and premium comfort-ready for your next adventure.
